{#
    A11y + action handling concept:
    -------------------------------

    Unfortunately this template is quite complex.
    Therefore I am trying to give a small rundown on how most things work in here,
    to make it easier to get a grasp of this video tile.

    We have two basic differences:
    a) The user can be the creator of the video
    b) The user just has access to the video.

    Our goals for case b) are:
    * The whole tile should be clickable and lead to the video player
    * The favor button should work correctly
    * Both elements should be reachable via tab presses
    * Pressing enter when these elements are in focus should trigger their respective
      action

    Case a)
    -------
    The tile has a drop down menu providing edit, delete and play actions.
    It also has the favor button in the top right edge of the tile.
    The actions panel is triggered by toggling a css class via javascript.
    The tile also has the favor button

    Case b)
    -------
    This tile does not have the actions dropdown menu. Instead it only has a
    title linking to the video player as well as the favor button.
    The whole tile itself is also clickable and leads to the video player.

    How does the favor button work?
    -------------------------------
    The favor button consists of multiple things:
    1. The favor button is a link (so favoring triggers a full page reload). We also added some JS to
       prevent the default click behavior of the parent tile (by stopping propagation)

    How does the click on the tile work?
    ------------------------------------
    We attach a click and an on keypress handler via JS to the tile itself.
    In both events we programmatically click the title link.
    If a user tabs, they will directly land on the title link and will therefore be able
    to press enter to navigate to the video player.
#}

{% if is_granted('edit', video.data) %}
    <div
        tabindex="0"
        id="tile-{{ video.data.id }}"
        class="tile"
        title="{{ video.data.description }}"
        data-test-id="video-tile--{{ video.data.id }}"
    >
        <input id="{{ video.data.id }}" type="checkbox" />
        <label for="{{ video.data.id }}" class="tile__content">
            <img alt="Vorschaubild" class="tile__image" src="{{ video.data.encodedVideoDirectory | virtualized_file_url }}/thumbnail.jpg"/>
            <span class="tile__date">{{ video.data.createdAt|date("d.m.Y") }}</span>
            <span class="tile__title">
                {% if video.data.courses | length == 0 %}
                    <i class="fas fa-eye-slash" title="Video ist privat"></i>
                {% endif %}
                {{ video.data.title }}
            </span>
            <i class="tile__action-icon fas fa-arrow-down"></i>
        </label>
        {% if app.user.isStudent %}
            {{ _self.favorButton(video) }}
        {% endif %}
        <div class="tile__actions">
            <a href="{{ path('mediathek__video--player', {id: video.data.id}) }}">
                <i class="fas fa-play"></i> {% trans %}video.show.title{% endtrans %}
            </a>
            <a href="{{ path('mediathek__video--edit', {id: video.data.id}) }}">
                <i class="fas fa-pencil-alt"></i> {% trans %}video.edit.title{% endtrans %}
            </a>
            <a href="{{ path('mediathek__video--delete', {id: video.data.id}) }}" class="color-alert">
                <i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i> {% trans %}video.delete.title{% endtrans %}
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
{% else %}
    <div
        tabindex="0"
        class="tile"
        id="tile-{{ video.data.id }}"
        title="{{ video.data.description }}"
        data-location="{{ path("mediathek__video--player", {id: video.data.id}) }}"
    >
        <a tabindex="0" href="{{ path("mediathek__video--player", {id: video.data.id}) }}" class="tile__content">
            <img alt="Vorschaubild" class="tile__image" src="{{ video.data.encodedVideoDirectory | virtualized_file_url }}/thumbnail.jpg"/>
            <span class="tile__date">{{ video.data.createdAt|date("d.m.Y") }}</span>
            <span class="tile__title">{{ video.data.title }}</span>
            <i class="tile__action-icon fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
        {% if app.user.isStudent %}
            {{ _self.favorButton(video) }}
        {% endif %}
    </div>
{% endif %}

{% macro favorButton(video)  %}
    {% if video.isFavorite %}
        <a
            href="{{ path('mediathek__video--favor', {id: video.data.id}) }}"
            class="tile__favor-button"
            title="{% trans %}video.unfavor.title{% endtrans %}"
            data-test-id="tile__favor-button-{{ video.data.id }}"
        >
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star-sharp" data-test-id="remove-video-from-favorites--{{ video.data.id }}"></i>
        </a>
    {% else %}
        <a
            href="{{ path('mediathek__video--favor', {id: video.data.id}) }}"
            class="tile__favor-button"
            data-test-id="tile__favor-button-{{ video.data.id }}"
            title="{% trans %}video.favor.title{% endtrans %}"
        >
            <i class="fa-regular fa-star-sharp" data-test-id="add-video-to-favorites--{{ video.data.id }}"></i>
        </a>
    {% endif %}
{% endmacro %}
